">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂。</span>"},{"pid":"4ab40fa8121585fc4ff27379c56ed3f8e506ad4c","tid":1728798,"uid":249885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:33:35.000Z","msg":"非法集結worrr"},{"pid":"fdccd82e36aaec0e550e0ae8dca34f6f04e32e38","tid":1728798,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:37:38.000Z","msg":"今時今日應該所有黑警都知道啲催淚彈有幾毒，咁都仲放，佢哋到底有無人性？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1728933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1728933</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fbef44a13c5cc7e89f2b851cc62b5fbc27d12129","tid":1728798,"uid":317188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cba00aacfbae0763fea749de5d52ab3ae3544af","tid":1728798,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />九龍城碼頭，北角增兵，紅土，藍地，自殺式攞文宣"}]}